{"id":554330,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/03/【图说天朝】大·宝剑/","date":"2017-03-18T07:16:25Z","modified":"2017-03-18T07:54:14Z","title":"【图说天朝】大·宝剑","content":"<p><strong><a href=\"http://slide.mil.news.sina.com.cn/slide_8_203_49166.html#p=1\" target=\"_blank\">新浪军事｜纪念3.14海战：中国海军舰长政委开始佩长剑了</a></strong></p>\n<blockquote><p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/203_245428_796247.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-554334\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/203_245428_796247.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"505\" height=\"297\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/203_245428_796247.jpg 950w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/203_245428_796247-300x177.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/203_245428_796247-768x452.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/203_245428_796247-80x48.jpg 80w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 505px) 100vw, 505px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/203_245425_726552.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-554337\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/203_245425_726552.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"505\" height=\"301\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/203_245425_726552.jpg 950w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/203_245425_726552-300x179.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/203_245425_726552-768x458.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/203_245425_726552-80x48.jpg 80w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 505px) 100vw, 505px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/203_245432_818085.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-554336\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/203_245432_818085.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"505\" height=\"369\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/203_245432_818085.jpg 950w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/203_245432_818085-300x219.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/203_245432_818085-768x561.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 505px) 100vw, 505px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/203_245426_885467.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-554332\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/203_245426_885467.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"505\" height=\"266\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/203_245426_885467.jpg 950w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/203_245426_885467-300x158.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/203_245426_885467-768x405.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 505px) 100vw, 505px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/203_245429_658038.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-554335\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/203_245429_658038.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"505\" height=\"282\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/203_245429_658038.jpg 950w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/203_245429_658038-300x168.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/203_245429_658038-768x429.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 505px) 100vw, 505px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/203_245431_249282.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-554339\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/203_245431_249282.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"505\" height=\"338\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/203_245431_249282.jpg 950w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/203_245431_249282-300x201.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/203_245431_249282-768x513.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 505px) 100vw, 505px\" /></a></p>\n<p>据当代海军报道，3月15日上午，南海舰队某驱护支队举行合格的舰长政委一起被授予“深蓝之剑”。[&#8230;]宝剑旨在纪念3.14海战，砥砺官兵不忘初心，继续前进。</p>\n<p>三亚舰舰长王先军一袭白衣，立于舰首，手中的花纹钢长剑离了乌木鞘，寒光凛凛。</p>\n<p>仪式上，这群来自国产最新型驱护舰的主官们手持宝剑、面向军旗，发出誓言。</p>\n<p>誓言16个字：聚气凝魂、忠烈断金、练胆励性、誓比打赢、剑指深蓝、舍我其谁。</p>\n<p><strong>“深蓝之剑”寄托深远：</strong></p>\n<p>剑长0.8米，时刻提醒持剑者牢记支队担负的8项使命任务。</p>\n<p>刃宽3.14厘米，旨在纪念3.14海战，砥砺官兵不忘初心，继续前进。</p>\n<p>柄长12.26厘米，意为支队是12月26日成立，同时也是支队战舰出征海军首批亚丁湾护航行动的日子。</p>\n<p>被授予人的姓名刻于剑刃之上，体现宝剑的独一无二和对被授予人的激励。</p></blockquote>\n<p><strong>以下评论由数字时代编辑收集自新浪微博：</strong></p>\n<p>@薯片你又不正经了：大。。。大宝剑<img title=\"[doge]\" src=\"http://img.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/b6/doge_org.gif\" alt=\"[doge]\" /></p>\n<p>@丽竞门少卿：局座说海军要有百年的文化沉淀。这大宝剑一出，直接千年了！</p>\n<p>@海上闲云鹤：太难看了，不中不洋的拿把汉剑。</p>\n<p>@嘿嘿嘿嘿嘿嘿嘿嘿嘿嘿哈哈哈哈：其实应该配金箍棒，个人觉得比较帅，或者是方天画戟，青龙偃月也不错，哈哈哈哈哈</p>\n<p>@看起来很学术的王啸宇：满满的皇帝御林军的感觉<img title=\"[笑cry]\" src=\"http://img.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/34/xiaoku_org.gif\" alt=\"[笑cry]\" /><img title=\"[笑cry]\" src=\"http://img.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/34/xiaoku_org.gif\" alt=\"[笑cry]\" /><img title=\"[笑cry]\" src=\"http://img.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/34/xiaoku_org.gif\" alt=\"[笑cry]\" /></p>\n<blockquote><p><strong>@秋津洲改: 这么一说，辐射4还是挺考据的。</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/9dda3dcegy1fdqyuxsjafj20ok0cvqd3.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-554331\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/9dda3dcegy1fdqyuxsjafj20ok0cvqd3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"505\" height=\"264\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/9dda3dcegy1fdqyuxsjafj20ok0cvqd3.jpg 884w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/9dda3dcegy1fdqyuxsjafj20ok0cvqd3-300x157.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/03/9dda3dcegy1fdqyuxsjafj20ok0cvqd3-768x402.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 505px) 100vw, 505px\" /></a></p></blockquote>\n<p>@您身边的深海用户:这么奇奇怪怪罗里吧嗦的东西 是不是义乌订的货啊？</p>\n<p>@康庄大：袁世凯称帝感强烈。</p>\n<p><strong>【附】</strong></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_554344\" style=\"width: 410px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"h